  "informal_statement": "A sum over range (n+1) peels off the last term f n: the recursion underlying inductive sum proofs.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Directly `Finset.sum_range_succ`.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem sum_range_succ' (f : ℕ → ℕ) (n : ℕ) : (∑ i ∈ Finset.range (n + 1), f i) = (∑ i ∈ Finset.range n, f i) + f n",
